      <comment>r2.7.1) (robot Adding: [[ru:Дэвид Фридман]]</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Other people2|David Friedman (disambiguation)}}
{{Infobox economist
| name             = David Director Friedman
| school_tradition = [[Chicago School of Economics]]
| color            = maroon
| image       = Davidfriedmanatcato.jpg
