      <minor />
      <comment>r2.6.4) (robot Modifying: [[fr:Aneth]]</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{about|the herb}}
{{taxobox
|name = Dill
|image = Illustration Anethum graveolens0.jpg
|regnum = [[Plantae]]
|unranked_divisio = [[Angiosperms]]
|unranked_classis = [[Eudicots]]
|unranked_ordo = [[Asterids]]
|ordo = [[Apiales]]
